

## 📊 Academic Dashboard & Progress Visualization

ExamBud provides a real-time, interactive dashboard that converts learning activity into clear, actionable insights.
It serves as a centralized control system for tracking progress, managing time, and executing study tasks.

---

### 🧭 Subject Mastery

* Radial progress indicators for each subject
* Percentage-based mastery representation
* Color-coded levels:

  * Green → Strong understanding
  * Yellow → Moderate progress
  * Red → Needs improvement
* Smooth updates based on real-time performance

---

### ⏱️ Study Timer

* Central countdown timer for focused sessions
* Displays active subject and task
* Supports structured study methods (e.g., Pomodoro)
* Visual urgency indicators as time approaches completion

---

### 📌 Active Focus

* Highlights the current subject or task
* Keeps the user anchored to a single objective
* Reduces context switching and distraction

---

### 📋 Task Management

* Structured daily task cards with:

  * Topic
  * Description
  * Learning objective

* Status states:

  * Completed
  * In Progress
  * Incomplete
  * Deferred

* Visual prioritization based on importance

---

### 📈 Real-Time Feedback

* Updates dynamically based on user activity
* Adjusts mastery levels automatically
* Surfaces weak areas for targeted improvement

---

### 🧭 Navigation Taskbar

A floating taskbar provides quick access to core features without interrupting workflow.

* Appears contextually and remains hidden when not needed

* Enables fast navigation across:

  * Home
  * Tasks
  * Calendar
  * Study Modules
  * Notes
  * Settings

* Designed with a minimal, icon-based interface

* Uses subtle visual feedback for interaction

---

### 🎨 Interface Design

* Dark theme optimized for long study sessions
* Clean layout with minimal distractions
* Smooth transitions and interaction feedback
* Consistent visual hierarchy across components

---

### 🧠 Design Principles

* Immediate feedback improves engagement
* Visible progress increases motivation
* Time awareness improves discipline
* Focused workflow reduces cognitive overload

---

### 🔥 Summary

The dashboard acts as a real-time academic control layer, helping students:

* Monitor progress
* Maintain focus
* Manage study time
* Improve weak areas efficiently

